data.title: Graduation Master Brochure May 2022 Web
data.meta_description: Graduation Master Brochure May 2022 Web - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides information about the academic dress code and order of proceedings for a University of Nottingham graduation ceremony. It includes the colors and styles of gowns and hoods for different degrees as well as the musical program. The ceremony will begin with processions of academic staff and honored guests before degrees are conferred. The presiding officer will open and close the congregation.
